1 (5) It is the intent of the Legislature to appropriate one million
2 dollars for fiscal year 2025-26 and one million dollars for fiscal year
3 2026-27 from the Opioid Treatment Infrastructure Cash Fund to the Supreme
4 Court for medication-assisted treatment as provided in section 24-1302.
5 Sec. 3. Original sections 24-1302 and 71-2492, Revised Statutes
6 Cumulative Supplement, 2024, are repealed.
7 Sec. 4. Since an emergency exists, this act takes effect when
8 passed and approved according to law.
